data.title: Meet the Researchers
data.meta_description: Meet the researchers - short profiles on all our Dementia Researcher contributors working in all areas of discovery, from across the world
data.meta_site_name: DEMENTIA RESEARCHER - A network for early career researchers
data.text:
Trying to decide which career is right for you can be a complicated process. Whatever your reason for coming into the field, and whatever your area of discovery, we want to equip you with the right information to help you make the right decisions to help you progress your career and remain in dementia research.

On this page you will find profiles on all the people who have contributed to Dementia Researcher, sharing blogs, joining podcasts and presenting in webinars. Please use this page to find and connect with fellow researchers, reach out, share and collaborate.
